
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Information
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Biblestudy-Tool is used to do quick look-ups and note taking with references to 
the scriptures.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Requirements
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This needs MySQL server installed and running when the app starts up.  Derby is
used for the Bible text but MySQL is used for the Notes.  I'd like to remove 
that dependency, but for now, just have MySQL installed and running when .

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Open the projects in Eclipse.
2. Set your target platform to the one provided.
3. Do an export to whatever platform you need.
